            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a treatment method of crude sugar in chlorination neutralization liquid of sucralose-6-ester, and relates to the technical field of sucralose production. According to the method, trichloromethane is recycled firstly, and then DMF is recycled, so that the content of impurities in the obtained concentrated dry liquid is remarkably reduced, and the yield and purity of the obtained crude sugar are improved; according to the method, the pH value of the system is adjusted to 6-9 by using weak-base ammonia water, so that the condition that sucralose-6-ester is subjected to alkaline hydrolysis to generate sucralose due to too strong alkalinity is avoided, and the yield and the purity of crude sugar are improved. Moreover, the method provided by the invention does not need to consume a large amount of acid, hydrogen peroxide, organic solvent (in an oxidation reaction stage) and heat energy (multiple times of hot extraction), and the treatment cost of the chlorination neutralization solution is low. In addition, the treatment method provided by the invention can improve the conversion rate and daily productivity of sucralose-6-ester in the chlorination neutralization solution, reduce the output of wastewater and waste activated carbon, and is less in three wastes, low in energy consumption and low in production cost."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种三氯蔗糖‑6‑酯的氯化中和液中粗品糖的处理方法，涉及三氯蔗糖生产技术领域。本发明通过先回收三氯甲烷，之后回收DMF，显著降低了所得浓干液中的杂质含量，提高了所得粗品糖的收率和纯度；本发明利用弱碱氨水将体系的pH值调节至6～9，避免了碱性太强导致三氯蔗糖‑6‑酯碱解生成三氯蔗糖，提高了粗品糖的收率和纯度。而且，本发明提供的无需消耗大量的酸、双氧水、有机溶剂(氧化反应阶段)以及热能(多次热萃取)，氯化中和液的处理成本低。此外，本发明提供的处理方法能够提高氯化中和液中三氯蔗糖‑6‑酯的转化率和日产能，减少废水和废活性炭的产生量，三废少，能耗低，生产成本低。"
                }
            ]
